Class Coordinate

  • java.lang.Object
    • src.Coordinate

  • public class Coordinate
extends java.lang.Object
    Date: 23-11-2017 This class represents a point on earth using latitude & longitude. It calculates the distance between two points and returns if a specific point is within a given Km radius.
    Author:
    Kineret Ruth Nahary & Yakir Amar
